comments: Horford (BOS) raises his arm up to pursue the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Gobert's (MIN) left hand.
Tatum (BOS) and McDaniels (MIN) make incidental arm contact with one another after the loose ball is deflected toward them.
Anderson (MIN) initiates contact across Tatum's (BOS) right forearm, causing Tatum to lose control of the ball.
Brown (BOS) engages and disengages with Edwards (MIN) off-ball.
McDaniels (MIN) releases his off-arm away from Smart's (BOS) front after they come together during the drive and marginal contact occurs as McDaniels slows his momentum in the lane.
Smart (BOS) extends his right leg into McDaniels' (MIN) path and initiates foot-to-foot contact that affects McDaniels' SQBR.
Conley (MIN) briefly has his arms around Smart's (BOS) midsection before correcting.
McDaniels (MIN) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage with one another as Tatum moves to set the pick.
Tatum (BOS) extends his arms to the side and holds Conley's (MIN) upper half following the initial contact, affecting Conley's ability to go over the pick.
Smart (BOS) and Anderson (MIN) come together at the same spot off-ball and marginal contact occurs.
Gobert (MIN) brings his hands toward Tatum's (BOS) side and marginal contact occurs as Gobert releases away to roll.
Tatum (BOS) initiates contact across Gobert's (MIN) right arm during Gobert's upward shooting motion.
Brown (BOS) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Gobert (MIN) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) and Williams (BOS) engage and disengage with one another after the release of the jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) and Horford (BOS) engage and disengage with one another after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) and McDaniels (MIN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Brown (BOS) grasps and then quickly releases Gobert's (MIN) jersey after the release of the jump shot attempt and he does not affect his rebound positioning.
Edwards (MIN) briefly has his arm around Smart's (BOS) midsection before correcting.
Anderson (MIN) brings his right arm toward Brown's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs with Brown's front as Brown drives inside the perimeter.
Conley (MIN) brings his forearms toward Williams' (BOS) right side and marginal contact occurs as Williams retrieves the rebound.
McDaniels (MIN) and Gobert (MIN) initiate contact with Williams' (BOS) left and right arm, respectively, which causes Williams to lose control of the ball in the lane.
Williams (BOS) fumbles the ball and legally re-gains control of it along the baseline.
Prior to the whistled held ball, Gobert's (MIN) left foot is out of bounds when he makes contact with the ball.
Gobert (MIN) uses his left hand to make legal hand-on-ball contact and he ties Williams (BOS) up as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Williams' right arm. A jump ball is assessed.
Coach Mazzulla (BOS) enters the playing court and crosses the midcourt line.
Williams (BOS) tips the jump ball prior to it reaching its apex.
Horford (BOS) legally re-establishes his position without moving through the jumping circle.
Anderson (MIN) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Edwards (MIN) was ejected on one technical foul for directly questioning the integrity of the officiating crew.
Anderson (MIN) was ejected after being assessed his second technical foul for multiple profanities directed at the officiating crew.
Brown (BOS) legally contests Conley's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
